1:
Give praise to Yahweh, you sons of God!
\q Give praise to Yahweh for his glory and strength.
\q
2:
Give to Yahweh the glory that his name deserves.
\q Bow down to Yahweh in the splendor of holiness.
3:
The voice of Yahweh is heard over the waters;
\q the God of glory thunders,
\q Yahweh thunders over many waters.
\q
5:
The voice of Yahweh breaks the cedars;
\q Yahweh breaks in pieces the cedars of Lebanon.
6:
He makes Lebanon skip like a calf
\q and Sirion like a young ox.
\q
7:
The voice of Yahweh sends out flames of fire.
\q
8:
The voice of Yahweh shakes the wilderness;
\q Yahweh shakes the wilderness of Kadesh.
9:
The voice of Yahweh causes the oaks to twist
\q and strips the forests bare.
\q Everyone in his temple says, "Glory!"
\q
10:
Yahweh sits as king over the flood;
\q Yahweh sits as king forever.
11:
Yahweh gives strength to his people;
\q Yahweh blesses his people with peace.
